    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't want something \"new.\" there isn't anything new. there's just him. it feels like he's waiting for me somewhere, and the thought of being apart from him forever is what kills me. sometimes i think if i could just reach him, the silence wouldn't matter anymore. it would finally feel peaceful.",
